This list does not guarantee graduation. Any changes that need to be made should be done via Name Change Form, sent to graduation@uncp.edu, with one of the forms of ID listed on the Name Change Form.

If your name is not on this list or if you have further questions, please send an email to graduation@uncp.edu.
